author: Home Repair Tutor
description:
This video shows how to install a laundry tub faucet. You'll also see what tools to use and how to uninstall the old faucet. 

Visit https://homerepairtutor.com/laundry-faucet/ for more tips

#diy #homerepairtutor #plumbing   

How to Install a Laundry Tub Faucet
0:04 How to remove old laundry tub faucet
1:21 How to remove plumber's putty and rust from laundry tub
1:45 How to install new laundry tub faucet
2:22 How to install faucet water supply lines

These supplies were used in our video:

-WD-40 EZ Reach
-Milwaukee Basin Wrench
-Ridgid Faucet Tool
